<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= language === 'zh' ? 'zh-TW' : 'en' %>">
<head>
<!-- meta attributes -->
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="author" content="Jack Gowan">
<meta name="description" content="first built maze">
<title>The Maze - <%= language === 'zh' ? '迷宮' : 'The Maze' %></title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/a_maze_style.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="room-container">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="room-image">
          <img src="/images/a2_maze-touch-statue.png" alt="Touching the glowing statue">
        </div>
        <div class="room-content">
          <div class="room-text">
            <code>
            <%- translations?.[language]?.text || `<p>The statue is cold to touch. You press your ear up to it to better understand the soft breathing. You feel all around Ceres's head for a device.</p>
              <p>There is a loud thud behind you - one of the locked doors is being rammend from the inside - Something is trying to breakout!!</p>
              <p> You have no weapon and would be at a severe disadvantage.</p>  
              <p>What is your choice?</p>` %>
          </code>
          </div>

          <hr/>

          <div class="navigation">
          <p><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.prompt || 'Choose your path:' %></p>
          <a href="/maze/light-wait"><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.options?.[0] || 'Wait and fight' %></a>
          <a href="/maze/flee"><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.options?.[1] || 'Run like hell' %></a>
        </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
  </html>